{"tid":1085213,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"好耐無聽咁耐廣東歌 尋回從前的回憶","createTime":"2019-03-31T04:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T08:22:11.000Z","uid":147671,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc7be447db4fa20d88689ecc373c8a7674ae973","tid":1085213,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lPnxKYcoiQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-lPnxKYcoiQ&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP95R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=0011ffa3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lPnxKYcoiQ</a><br />\n無意中睇youtube睇到有人拍霹靂903歌托邦，睇到謝霆鋒昔日首首經典既歌，每聽一首都好有當年年輕既感覺，好似「壞習慣」咁已經係24年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間過得好快<br />\n<br />\n回頭一望香港樂壇仲剩低咩歌手可以咁有號召力？十隻手指都數得曬，要去大陸搵食既搵食，仍然堅持新歌出廣東歌既謝霆鋒，真係多謝你飲水思源，無放棄香港，雖然你曾經俾人笑mk鋒、扮廚師，但唔緊要。只要你有心促進返香港樂壇我地都歡迎你回來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地樂壇唔要吳業坤依d垃圾，我地要既係真正香港既天王巨星，真正能壓台既歌手，而唔係求其tvb搵個演員唱下歌既歌手，我地依十年食得太屎啦，真係好想廣東歌可以返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32df7f18e442ca2887150a401c95aecd6754dec0","tid":1085213,"uid":147671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"無巴絲有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb7696d121f8294e627e1e91f509bb2fddcfebf","tid":1085213,"uid":238437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"其實除咗tvb班所謂歌手，依幾年大把人出廣東歌啦，我覺得仲正過以前，只係你冇去聽，download個spptify去聽下啦"},{"pid":"cbfc2e6c1fb7ed0ac3f17200849faa32a702c9e6","tid":1085213,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb7696d121f8294e627e1e91f509bb2fddcfebf","tid":1085213,"uid":238437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:00:24.000Z","msg":"其實除咗tvb班所謂歌手，依幾年大把人出廣東歌啦，我覺得仲正過以前，只係你冇去聽，download個spptify去聽下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:58:41.